==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Forcer
<hw>For"cer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, forces or drives.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mech.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>The solid piston of
a force pump; the instrument by which water is forced in a pump.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>A small hand pump for sinking pits, draining cellars,
etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Forcible</ent>⟦br⟧
